from imblearn.over_sampling import SMOTE
smote = SMOTE(sampling_strategy='auto',          # 抽樣的策略
              random_state=None,                 # seed
              k_neighbors=5)                     # k 鄰近幾個點
X_train_smote, y_train_smote = smote.fit_resample(X_train, y_train)

print("---【Original】----------")
print(Counter(y_train))
print("---【Smote】----------")

In [70]:
pca = PCA(n_components=2)  # 這裡降到 2 維
X_train_pca_2d = pca.fit_transform(X_train)
# 使用相同的 PCA 模型轉換測試集
X_test_pca_2d = pca.transform(X_test)


# 展示 PCA 結果
print("\n【轉換前後 X shape】")
shapes = {
    '轉換前 X': [X_train.shape, X_test.shape],
    '轉換後 X': [X_train_pca_2d.shape, X_test_pca_2d.shape]
}
shape_df = pd.DataFrame(shapes, index=['訓練集', '測試集'])
print(shape_df)

variance_df = pd.DataFrame({
    '主成分': [f'PC{i+1}' for i in range(len(pca.explained_variance_ratio_))],
    '解釋能力百分比': [f'{var*100:.2f}%' for var in pca.explained_variance_ratio_],
    '累積解釋能力百分比': [f'{var*100:.2f}%' for var in pca.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum()]
})
print("\n【主成分解釋能力的詳細表格】")
print(variance_df)

In [75]:
plt.figure(figsize=[5, 3])

plt.plot(range(1, len(pca_95.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum())+1), pca_95.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum(),
         linestyle="-", linewidth=1, color="red", marker=".")
plt.grid(True)
plt.xlabel("PC#", fontsize=9)
plt.ylabel("Explained Variance Ratio Cumsum", fontsize=9)
plt.title("Principal Component Analysis", fontsize=11)
plt.xticks(range(1, len(pca_95.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum())+1))

for x_, y_ in zip(range(1, len(pca_95.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum())+1), pca_95.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum()) :
    plt.text(x_, y_, f"{y_:.2%}", fontsize=7)


# 繪製選擇 PC 的總解釋百分比門檻值
plt.axhline(y=0.95, xmin=0, xmax=1, linestyle="--", linewidth=1, color="blue") # 以解釋率要到達多少去畫線
plt.show()

這裡可以看到從PC11到PC10瞬間解釋力降低很多 因此他選擇留下11個主成分 但11個其實真的有點多

T-SNE

降維2維 ( 使用原始數據 )

In [78]:
from sklearn.manifold import TSNE
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore', category=FutureWarning)

tsne = TSNE(
    n_components=2,    # 降維幾維
    n_iter=1000,       # 跌代次數
)
# t-SNE 沒有 transform 所以這裡只能先合併資料 後面再用index取得
X_all = np.concatenate([X_train, X_test], axis=0)
y_all = np.concatenate([y_train, y_test], axis=0)
X_all_tsne = tsne.fit_transform(X_all)

X_train_tsne_2d = X_all_tsne[:len(X_train), :]  # 訓練集的降維結果
X_test_tsne_2d = X_all_tsne[len(X_train):, :]  # 測試集的降維結果

print("\n【tsne 轉換前後 X shape】")
shapes = {
    '轉換前 X': [X_train.shape, X_test.shape],
    '轉換後 X': [X_train_tsne_2d.shape, X_test_tsne_2d.shape]
}
shape_df = pd.DataFrame(shapes, index=['訓練集', '測試集'])
print(shape_df)

    n_components=2,    # 降維幾維
    n_iter=1000,       # 跌代次數
)
# t-SNE 沒有 transform 所以這裡只能先合併資料 後面再用index取得
X_all = np.concatenate([X_train_smote, X_test], axis=0)
y_all = np.concatenate([y_train_smote, y_test], axis=0)
X_all_tsne = tsne.fit_transform(X_all)

X_smote_train_tsne_2d = X_all_tsne[:len(X_train_smote), :]  # 訓練集的降維結果
X_smote_test_tsne_2d = X_all_tsne[len(X_train_smote):, :]  # 測試集的降維結果

print("\n【tsne 轉換前後 X shape】")
shapes = {
    '轉換前 X': [X_train_smote.shape, X_test.shape],
    '轉換後 X': [X_smote_train_tsne_2d.shape, X_smote_test_tsne_2d.shape]
}
shape_df = pd.DataFrame(shapes, index=['訓練集', '測試集'])
print(shape_df)

from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

def train_and_evaluate(X_train_list, X_test_list, y_train_list, y_test_list, names_list):
    accuracies = []
    for X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test, name in zip(X_train_list, X_test_list, y_train_list, y_test_list, names_list):
        # 訓練邏輯回歸模型
        model = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000)
        model.fit(X_train, y_train)
        y_pred = model.predict(X_test)
        accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)
        accuracies.append(accuracy)
        model.fit(X_train, y_train)
        print(f'【 {name} 】')
        print(f"train acc : {model.score(X_train, y_train):.2%}")
        print(f"test acc : {model.score(X_test, y_test):.2%}")
        print("===========================")
    return accuracies

accuracies = train_and_evaluate(X_train_list, X_test_list, y_train_list, y_test_list, names_list)

📈Summary¶

  1. 從這裡可以看出來 前面雖然主成分經過資料不平衡處理後，主成分累積解釋能力百分比些許提升，但後續進入模型後表現不佳，因此這裡後續不會再對他做資料不平衡的處理。
  2. 就整體而言【 PCA 95% 11D 】模型表現最好，選擇保留較多主成分有助於提高模型，甚至還比原先的模型高出一些些。
  3. 【 t-SNE 2D 】僅僅保留了兩個維度，雖然表現不如【 PCA 95% 11D 】，但2D可以有效降低計算複雜度，如果資料更需要可視化和查看不同類別的分布時，可以選擇這個模型。

經過各種模型的比較，最終選擇【PCA 95% 11D】模型，因為它能在保持較高解釋能力的同時，顯著提高模型準確度，並且在實際應用中具有良好的表現。
